40 become a permitted payment stablecoin issuer under G.S. 53-463(f) or cease offering its payment
41 stablecoin in this State and shall provide holders of the payment stablecoin notice of their
42 redemption rights.
43 SECTION 2.(e) This section becomes effective the earlier of January 18, 2027, or
